Message: My conversion tag is not getting accepted

I'm sorry to hear that your conversion tag is not getting accepted. Could you please let me know which platform or service you are using for the conversion tag? This will help me provide more specific instructions.
google tag

Thanks for letting me know you're using Google Tag Manager. To install a NewsBreak Pixel with GTM, follow these steps:
1. Click the 'Tags' option in the left-hand sidebar, then click the 'New' button.
2. Give this tag a meaningful name (e.g., NewsBreak Pixel Conversion Code), then click on the box to open a list with all available tag types.
3. Choose 'Custom HTML' from the list and a blank text box will appear where you can input scripts.
4. In your NewsBreak Ad Manager Event Tracking Tool, copy the NewsBreak Pixel conversion code under section 2.
5. Paste the code into the blank text box in GTM.
6. Click the box to create a new trigger or use an existing one for NewsBreak conversion pixel.
For more detailed instructions, you can refer to this article: [How to install a NewsBreak Pixel with GTM](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/14333966189581-How-to-install-a-NewsBreak-Pixel-with-GTM). Let me know if you need any further assistance!
